description:
Demolition of all existing built-form and structures on the Site and associated site clearance and remediation works to provide a clear, uncontaminated site;
Construction of a c. 20 storey office building comprising c. 5,858 sqm (GIA) of high-quality café, coworking and office floorspace, including a proportion of affordable workspace, that represents a significant uplift on the existing building and the quantum of employment opportunities available;
State-of-the-art fit out, adopting the highest levels of sustainability that strives to meet the maximum levels of accreditation in this regard;
 Implementation of a high quality design with active frontages and enhancement to the adjoining public realm, which is sensitive to and responds positively to the character and appearance of the area; and Provides a significant improvement to the existing destination facilities, which include ample cycle parking, employee facilities and servicing areas, located at basement level.
site visit/meeting and written advice: £10,720.00 + VAT = £12,864.00
